{"tid":616723,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【四月新番】立花館戀愛三角關係","createTime":"2018-04-04T11:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T18:31:55.000Z","uid":135110,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"add865474a2edca0da6f5b008406c48c311971e0","tid":616723,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/193429_0564d4ec4885448fc55b26b11c1ae743.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F193429_0564d4ec4885448fc55b26b11c1ae743.png&h=65ce41dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《立花館戀愛三角關係》描述剛搬進立花館的第一天，夏乃花火就遇到了神秘的全裸美少女，還不小心看到成熟大姊姊害羞的地方，又在陰錯陽差之下，凝視著不給她好臉色看的兒時玩伴的&hellip;？面對如此的狀況，花火下定決心等一個月的租約結束之後，絕對要搬出去！<br />\n■ STAFF <br />\n原作：merryhachi <br />\n總監督：ひらさわひさよし <br />\n系列構成：WORDS in STEREO <br />\n角色設計：花井柚都子 <br />\n動畫製作：：Creators in pack / STUDIO LINGS<br />\n<br />\n■ CAST <br />\n夏乃花火：津田美波<br />\n藤原香菓：櫻木亞美紗<br />\n篁伊織：仲田亞里沙<br />\n藤原依子：松嵜麗<br />\n月城優：小松未可子<br />\n三井苑愛：喜多村英梨<br />\n<br />\n■ INFO <br />\n放送日期：4 月 3 日 <br />\n每週更新：星期三</div>"},{"pid":"fd82f9cedd423496d8fa1f409f0f328913d9c4a0","tid":616723,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解冇人開po"},{"pid":"fbcff4c8266c4b01ae591f71a90cd3d933f98caa","tid":616723,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/202049_f94c37f0201c1d3a7d046fecc1f3d137.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F202049_f94c37f0201c1d3a7d046fecc1f3d137.png&h=fea54644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/202047_25f07f885286e02b4649d1e0a30e36a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li